7 ché la gente che fonde a goccia a goccia 8 per li occhi il mal che tutto ’l mondo occupa, 9 da l’altra parte in fuor troppo s’approccia.

query.result:
**English:**
4 I moved, and my guide moved with me through 5 the rapid places, right along the rock, 6 as one goes along a narrow wall to the battlements;
7 for the people who distil drop by drop 8 through their eyes the evil that infects the world, 9 on the other side draw too near.
