**English:**

112 Then we accuse Sapphira with her husband;
113 I praise the kicks that Heliodorus got;
114 and throughout the mountain Polymnestor
115 who slew Polydorus is reviled;
116 finally we are shouted at: “Crassus,
117 tell us, for you know: what does gold taste like?”

